  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t亡羊补牢 尤未为晚： 习大马棒亲爹故乡开始成立研究习大马棒思维著作研究所啦：<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9WWGlnSkZOLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/VXigJFN.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/VXigJFN.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VXigJFN.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n这真是：<br/>\r\n文盲跪过流氓<br/>\r\n流氓反学文盲<br/>\r\n黄俄舔着白俄<br/>\r\n白俄要拜黄俄<br/>\r\n当年杀华无穷<br/>\r\n血染长白冻土<br/>\r\n如今孽债全忘<br/>\r\n狼狈为奸合伙。<br/>\n<br/>\n<b><a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/38242\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/38242\">乱世笑林</a>。<a href=\"https://www.pincong.rocks/article/3106\" title=\"https://www.pincong.rocks/article/3106\">习大马棒著作：康熙字典勘误</a>。</b> </div>",
